OL,3,CCouncil launches High Court bid over
OL,4,Cflags on highways
OL,6,FOxfordshire County Council has
OL,7,Flaunched a legal bid to prevent flags
OL,8,Fbeing placed on public roads.
OL,10,FThe council is set to ask the High
OL,11,FCourt in London to grant an injunction
OL,12,Fto prevent the unauthorised placement
OL,13,Fof the flags on or near highways,
OL,14,Fsaying that this has involved safety
OL,15,Frisks, as well as trespass and
OL,16,Fobstruction.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
