CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781777898
OL,3,CCouncil launches High Court bid over
OL,4,Cflags on highways
OL,6,FThe local authority also said on
OL,7,FWednesday that residents and council
OL,8,Fstaff have faced harassment or
OL,9,Fconfrontation when flags have been
OL,10,Fremoved.
OL,12,FThe widespread flying of Union and St
OL,13,FGeorge's Cross flags, following an
OL,14,Fonline campaign called Operation Raise
OL,15,Fthe Colours, has become contentious
OL,16,Fand several local authorities have
OL,17,Fremoved them from public
OL,18,Finfrastructure.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781777898
OL,3,CCouncil launches High Court bid over
OL,4,Cflags on highways
OL,6,FWhile some politicians decried the
OL,7,Fremovals, others claimed the increased
OL,8,Fnumber being flown was a result of
OL,9,Fxenophobia or racism.
OL,11,FOxfordshire County Council said flags
OL,12,Fhave been placed on or near public
OL,13,Froads without permission for months,
OL,14,Fdespite a formal legal notice in March
OL,15,Fand pre-action legal letters sent to
OL,16,Findividuals last month.
OL,18,FThe case is now due to be heard at the
OL,19,FHigh Court on June 23, the authority
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
