FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781777898
OL,3,CCouncil launches High Court bid over
OL,4,Cflags on highways
OL,6,FCouncil leader Tim Bearder said: "This
OL,7,Fapplication is about protecting our
OL,8,Fresidents, our workforce and the
OL,9,Fvalues we stand for as a county.
OL,11,F"We are proud of Oxfordshire's diverse
OL,12,Fcommunities and of our Council of
OL,13,FSanctuary status.
OL,15,F"We proudly fly the Union flag and St
OL,16,FGeorge's flag at County Hall and we
OL,17,Ffully support the right of residents
OL,18,Fto display flags on their own private
OL,19,Fproperty.
OL,26,@nD@bOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781777898
OL,3,CCouncil launches High Court bid over
OL,4,Cflags on highways
OL,6,F"However, there's an important
OL,7,Fdistinction between lawful expression
OL,8,Fand activity that puts people at risk
OL,9,For intimidates residents in their own
OL,10,Fcommunities.
OL,12,F"This activity is not about national
OL,13,Fpride or unity.
OL,15,F"It is unlawful behaviour, which has
OL,16,Fcaused fear and division within our
OL,17,Fcommunities.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
